metadata.name: I died but I survived #1
metadata.description: I am 52 years old on June 15th 2022 I took 40 white Tylenol pills and 40 blue Tylenol pills all at once in an effort to end my life . At that moment with all that was happening in my life I thought it was my only option which I later realizes was not but at that moment I was so overwhelmed I thought it was. Had it not been for my aunt a good friend and those ambulance drivers I would not be here today . I sent 7 days in the ICU then another 7 days in the psych ward I came home on the 28th . I am appreciative of being alive and I am doing an NFT project called I died but I survived . I have already contacted the American suicide prevention foundation about what I’m doing . My intention is to produce 800 NFTs selling for 1ETH each 40% percent goes to them and other organizations that help person with mental health issues that may want to end their life, another 50000USD in eth goes to a volunteer ambulance organization to either refurbish or towards buy an ambulance if it’s enough as without them I’m not here 10% goes back to buyers in a one off raffle. Plus a merch store where 50 percent of proceeds goes towards helping those who may want to end their life, If I can at least save one life with this it helps ,Thank you
